# npm install failed
- temporary use
```cmd
npm --registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org install packagename
```
- persistent use
```cmd
npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org

# validate
npm config get registry
```

# idea can not recognition /src alias '@'
- Languages & Frameworks -> JavaScript -> webpack
- choose your webpack.base.conf.js
- Languages & Frameworks -> Node.js and NPM
- check Coding assistance for Node.js 

# why bind keyup, not keydown or keypress
```javascript
  window.addEventListener('keydown', function (ev) {
    console.log(`trigger keydown event:${ev}`)
    // preview bind here will loss the first char you input, 
    // because the char you entered have not pass into the editor.
  })

  window.addEventListener('keypress', function (ev) {
    console.log(`trigger keypress event: ${ev}`)
    // same to the keydown
  })
```
- [different in key event](https://blog.csdn.net/john1337/article/details/46980913)
